    • Constructor Detail

      • PreparedStatementCache

        public PreparedStatementCache(IfxSqliConnect connection,
                      int maximumEntries)
        Creates a new LRU map based on a LinkedHashMap that supports an upper-limit on the number of entries. The eldest (oldest) entry in the map will be removed when the maximum number of entries allowed is exceeded.
        Parameters:
        maximumKEntries - the maximum number of entries to allow in the LRU map
